api_list.name: Get all SMI stocks
api_list.description: This endpoint retrun all stocks from SMI. Current Value will uodate everery 15min.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://stockfinder_api.p.rapidapi.com/smi"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "stockfinder_api.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
